# --- 1. PYTHON GARBAGE ---
**/venv/
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc
# Created by master_automation.py during --dry-run
**/_dry_run_output/

# --- 2. HEAVY DATA / SECRETS ---
# Ignore the encrypted vault
**/vaults.hc
# Ignore sensitive env files
.env
**/.env
dockcheck.config
# Created by run.sh during the "Handoff" phase
.temp_env_handoff

# --- 3. LOGS & TEMP ---
**/_logs/
**/*.log
**/*.tmp
**/*.bak
**/status_dashboard.md
**/status.json
# Ignore ALL symlinks to the vault
**/vaults/
**/2fa/
**/backups/

# --- 4. OS JUNK ---
.DS_Store
